<p>Evergreen content is not a tactic. It is the foundation of a content strategy that builds real business value over time. The businesses that dominate organic search in 2026 and beyond are the ones treating their content library as an asset. Writing once, ranking for years, and compounding their advantage with every update cycle.</p>
<p>Start with one evergreen guide on your most important topic. Build the cluster around it. Measure, update, and repeat.</p>
